title: Sound of the 70's - Come on Feel the Noise

sources.title: Sound of the 70's - Come on Feel the Noise
sources.description:
Dive into the 1970's classic hits from Squeeze, Steve Harley & Cockney Rebel, John Martyn, 10cc, Medicine Head, The Stranglers, LuLu & David Bowie, Slade, Natalie Cole, New York Dolls, Tom Robinson, Tim Buckley, The Three Degrees, A Taste of Honey, David Cassidy

Alongside archival footage, this volume showcases how these artists both responded to and influenced the cultural shifts of the 1970s. Their music became the soundtrack for a generation.

Director: Jason Fenwick
Year 2021
